   "state" : "closed",
   "body" : "Continues from #1351; fixes #1495\r\n\r\n- [x] Implemented @chrismorast's design:\r\n![screenshot - 02082015 - 02 56 53 pm](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/4411471/6098117/dc4f0096-afa2-11e4-9a85-b82606aacb74.png)\r\n![687474703a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f483658504c51512e706e67](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/5282264/6124591/ae6aaa56-b149-11e4-97b5-c70acef3bbe9.png)\r\n- [x] shortcode input (like `#aaa`) works\r\n- [x] use the number input on mobile (that's a third party keyboard):\r\n![687474703a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f47575850736d372e706e67](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/5282264/6124597/b4745d8e-b149-11e4-9a29-b2d9abfdf9bb.png)\r\n- [x] correct dismissing of keyboard on mobile\r\n- [x] moved assets out of subdirectory (depending on duckduckgo/p5-app-duckpan#136)\r\n- [x] IE8 `filter`\r\n- [x] test for specifying own color\r\n- [x] my attribution\r\n- [x] \"One thing I noticed in the palette selector is that the colors are incorrect. How is that being generated?\" <-- I think this has to do with [this](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CMYK_color_model#mediaviewer/File:CIE1931xy_gamut_comparison.svg); some colors cannot be represented in all of RGB, CMYK, and HSV.\r\n- [x] Event handlers could be consolidated.\r\n\r\nSorry for the huge screenshots! cc @moollaza @jagtalon @MrChrisW @chrisharrill ",
